	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">A combat unit is any unit able to attack in melee or ranged combat. The attack may be directed at another combat unit, a non-combat unit, or a city or outpost. Non-military units such as Workers, Colonists or Trade Convoys may not initiate an attack. Only certain orbital units may initiate combat. All aliens are considered combat units.</div>
